STATE
v.
Danny Corey WILLIAMS 351P19-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 5, 2019 Danny Corey Williams, For Williams, Danny Corey N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, For the State of North Carolina

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 5th of September 2019 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of September 2019."
